I"z<p>Saya berharap disini sudah melakukan instalasi mysql pada server / machine yang digunakan. Jika belum coba lihat dokumentasi <a href="https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-mysql-on-centos-7">berikut</a>  untuk melakukan instalasi mysql pada CentOS.</p>

<h3 id="1-membuat-user--dengan-previlages">1. Membuat User  dengan previlages</h3>
<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>mysql <span class="nt">-u</span> root <span class="nt">-p</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<blockquote>
  <p>CREATE USER ‘fawzi’@’localhost’ IDENTIFIED BY ‘P@ssw0rd’;
CREATE USER ‘fawzi’@’%’ IDENTIFIED BY ‘P@ssw0rd’;
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON <em>.</em> TO ‘fawzi’@’localhost’ WITH GRANT OPTION;
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON <em>.</em> TO ‘fawzi’@’%’ WITH GRANT OPTION;
flush privileges</p>
